file.name: openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: Exampled API
  description: No description available
  version: v1
servers:
  - url: /serviceName/client-api/v1
    description: The server
tags:
  - name: examples
paths:
  /null:
    description: not implemented

components:
  schemas:
    SingleReference:
      $ref: '#/components/schemas/direct'
    DirectReference:
      $ref: '#/components/schemas/direct'
    direct:
      description: direct
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
      required:
        - id
    directer:
      description: directer
      type: object
      properties:
        code:
          type: string
          description: directors code
      required:
        - code
    nesting:
      type: object
      properties:
        internal:
          type: object
          properties:
            nested:
              type: object
              description: nested
              properties:
                nestedId:
                  type: string
                  description: nested id
    DoubleReference:
      $ref: '#/components/schemas/DirectReference'
    ReferencingProperties:
      type: object
      properties:
        direct:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/DirectReference'
        doubleReference:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/DoubleReference'
        myOwn:
          description: myOwn
          type: boolean
    Composite:
      description: Composite
      type: object
      properties:
        ofMyOwn:
          type: boolean
      allOf:
        - $ref: '#/components/schemas/direct'
        - $ref: '#/components/schemas/directer'
      required:
        - ofMyOwn
    Array:
      type: array
      items:
        $ref: '#/components/schemas/direct'
    ReferencingOtherComponentsProperty:
      type: object
      properties:
        myCode:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/directer/properties/code'
        myNested:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/nesting/properties/internal/properties/nested/properties/nestedId'
        myDirect:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Array/items'
